Schemas

Schemas location
<people schemaLocation="https://www.hills.ccsf.edu/my.xsd">

the xsd file would affect the whole file
  <name>John</name>
    <age schemaLocation=...>18<age>
</people>

How to use external schemas
1.) using css
2.) transform XML ti XSL (Extended StyleSheet Language)
3.) transfer XML to HTML
XML -> XSLT -> XSL ->HTML

INPUT - XML -> XSLT Processor -> output - XSL 
Abbas like XSLT Processor name -> Saxon.sourceforge.net

<H3> hello </H3> HTML -> header
<H3> hello </H3> XML -> nothing 
